reaction to recent losses. The dollar was higher against the yen. The Nikkei
Stock Average gained 225.28 points, or 1.40 percent, to 16,265.51 at the end of
the morning session. In New York, the Dow rose 37.74 points to 11,233.23 at
Tuesday's close. The Nasdaq fell 46.84 points to end at 3,849.51.
</P>
