and Juan Pierre's run-scoring groundout.
</P>
<P>
   Jeff Frye went 4-for-4 and scored three runs.
</P>
<P>
   The Rockies took a 2-1 lead in the third after Frye led off with
a single, was sacrificed to second by Yoshii and went to third on
Nefi Perez's bunt single.
</P>
<P>
