walk to Helton loaded the bases. Clement then hit Jeffrey Hammonds
with his first pitch to give Colorado a 2-1 lead.
</P>
<P>
   Ben Petrick reached on Dave Magadan's throwing error to lead off
the Colorado fourth and Frye followed with an infield single.
Yoshii sacrificed the runners and Pierre beat out an infield single
to second base that scored Petrick.
