   On the Net: Senate Commerce Committee site:
http://www.senate.gov/(tilde)commerce
</P>
<P>
   Federal Communications Commission site: http://www.fcc.gov
</P>
<P>
   Motion Picture Association of America site: http://www.mpaa.org
</P>
